ex:dataset_ami a sio:SIO_000089,
        dcat:Dataset ;
    dcterms:isReferencedBy <https://doi.org/10.1007/11677482_3> ;
    dcat:landingPage <https://groups.inf.ed.ac.uk/ami/corpus/> .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b0 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 ""^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b1 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 ""^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b10 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Okay , we've got half an hour for this one um to uh discuss the um functional design ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b11 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Could you plug me in ?"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b12 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "[other]"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b13 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "[laugh] Okay ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b14 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Thanks ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b15 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "All ready to go ?"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b16 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Okay ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b17 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Okay . [cough]"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b18 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Um so hopefully you've all been working away ,"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b19 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "and I've put the minutes of the last meeting in the project folder ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b2 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 ""^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b20 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Um so I guess just to to recap on uh what we did last time ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b21 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Um kind of uh got to know each other a little bit and uh got familiar with all the equipment"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b22 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "and started to discuss um a bit about the project , you know , cost-wise how much how much money we had to s"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b23 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Um just want to tell you that you have three new requirements ,"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b24 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "which is the  The first one [other] is that um uh the company's decided that teletext is outdated uh because of how popular the internet is ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b25 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Nobody uses teletext very much anymore ,"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b26 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "'Kay ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b27 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "so we don't really need to consider that in the functionality of the  of the remote control ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b28 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Um they've also suggested that we um we only use the remote control to control the television , not the V_C_R_ , D_V_D_ or anything else ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b29 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "I think the worry is that if the project becomes too complex then it'll affect um how long it takes us to get it into into production , the time to market ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b3 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 ""^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b30 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Okay ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b31 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "So um , we're just gonna keep it simple and it'll just control the T_V_ ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b32 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "And the other thing was that the company want the corporate colour and slogan to be implemented in the new design ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b33 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Um I'm not entirely sure what the corporate colour is ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b34 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "It might be yellow , because there seems to be a lot of yellow everywhere ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b35 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "And the slogan , like the actual written slogan , or just to embody the idea of the slogan ?"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b36 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Well that's the thing , I'm I'm not sure um"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b37 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "[other] uh th because on the the company website , uh what does it say "^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b38 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "'Bout putting the fashion in electronics ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b39 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Uh something "^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b4 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 ""^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b40 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Yeah ,"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b41 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Mm yeah ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b42 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "I mean do they  [other] Is that something they want actually written on it ,"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b43 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "'cause it's quite long ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b44 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Um or yeah , just the idea , but I'm not sure ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b45 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "So that's something we can discuss as well ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b46 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "So those are the three things ,"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b47 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "just not to worry about teletext , uh only control the T_V_ , and um and uh incorporate the uh colour and slogan of the company ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b48 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Um so is everybody okay with any of that"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b49 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 ", or do you want me to recap at all ?"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b5 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 ""^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b6 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Is that alright now ?"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b7 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "[other] Okay ."^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b8 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Sorry ?"^^xsd:string .

ex:utteranceTextES2002b9 a dido:UtteranceText ;
    sio:SIO_000300 "Okay , everybody all set to start the meeting ?"^^xsd:string .

